Description: Can Lady, Pearl and Diamond release the three legendary Pokemon in time to make a difference?
Title: POKEMON ADVENTURES, DIAMOND AND PEARL/PLATINUM, VOL. 8
Author: Hidenori Kusaka

Description: Issei Hyodo’s first date with Yuma Amano does end well. Instead of a goodnight kiss, she kills him! But his death is only the beginning, when he is reincarnated as a devil.
Title: HIGH SCHOOL DXD, VOL. 1
Author: Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima
Contributor: by Ichiei Ishibumi and Hiroji Mishima

Description: Yuichiro is on a mission to kill every vampire in existence but in order to accomplish his goal, he must become a master of demon-possessed weaponry.
Title: SERAPH OF THE END, VOL. 1
Author: Takaya Kagami and Yamato Yamamoto
Contributor: by Takaya Kagami and Yamato Yamamoto

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Crona goes on a killing spree in Moscow at the behest of Medusa. Will Maka be able to stop him?
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 20
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Toya is a teenage vampire who refuses to drink blood, even at the risk of his own health. He is also the only salvation for Chiyuki Matsuoka, who is diagnosed with heart problems, but will he agree to a bond that could heal them both?
Title: MILLENNIUM SNOW, VOL. 3
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: Black jumps at the opportunity to earn the final Pokemon badge he needs in order to become eligible for the Pokemon League.
Title: POKEMON BLACK AND WHITE, VOL. 16
Author: Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto
Contributor: by Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 3
Author: Okayado

Description: The Straw Hat crew set sail for the kingdom of Dressrosa, where they will attempt to take down Caesar Clown’s former boss, Doflamingo.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 71
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Nanami continue her search for the kami who cursed Tomoe, but her trip into the past contains more dangers than expected.
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 15
Author: Julietta Suzuki
